@DATABASE "Mission Elevator"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - M - Mission Elevator"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - M
                   ====================================

                              Mission Elevator
                              ================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(48724,0)"}          48724,0
@{"Infinite Time " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49855,0)"}          49855,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
